{"tid":1141913,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"十年幾老友，都不及金錢嘅誘惑","createTime":"2019-05-06T19:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T20:51:36.000Z","uid":207059,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38ae2d2841c8b5024802349787e783beef84bbb8","tid":1141913,"uid":207059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:54:53.000Z","msg":"友誼喺究竟值幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n我嘅朋友話我知， 6000就夠。<br />\n<br />\n呢三位「朋友」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地由小學識到依家，一直都係同一間學校，識咗十幾年都一直有見面敘舊。我一直都當佢地係最好嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n直到上個禮拜我生日就約咗佢地出嚟飲酒，酒吧就係佢地揀，然後叫嘢咩都由我話事，我當時冇留意，就求其叫咗幾支麥卡倫<br />\n<br />\n點知埋單嗰時，佢地居然問我點解叫d酒咁貴，大佬我撚知間bar咁撚貴咩又唔係我揀嘅，咁都算佢地居然要我包嗮成條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰刻我先知道自己係一條水魚。<br />\n<br />\n當然我當晚畀嗮成條數，因為我唔想同佢地吵，話嗮識咗咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n但係到頭嚟都係得我一個咁戇鳩，重視呢份友誼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03c54972db3d6aa3ac04266771806de8a459311","tid":1141913,"uid":118758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:56:39.000Z","msg":"屌 真係fd既自動自覺畀翻你啦"},{"pid":"69e81cdd4da8aef400767bbdbe7953b99d11c71d","tid":1141913,"uid":118758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:56:55.000Z","msg":"分手啦"},{"pid":"cce0b223fe133e140445953b6bdf905905aa25e3","tid":1141913,"uid":207059,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d03c54972db3d6aa3ac04266771806de8a459311","tid":1141913,"uid":118758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:56:39.000Z","msg":"屌 真係fd既自動自覺畀翻你啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:57:46.000Z","msg":"當冇咗件事，可能佢地覺得我醉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cd0bb8c2902119d49945ec101cef7882331f4d","tid":1141913,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:58:40.000Z","msg":"抵啦，好過比人呃十幾萬"},{"pid":"8078d1436ad6b93c2404ccead9ed50e142766476","tid":1141913,"uid":207059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0cd0bb8c2902119d49945ec101cef7882331f4d","tid":1141913,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:58:40.000Z","msg":"抵啦，好過比人呃十幾萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"十幾萬買唔買到友情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff2a51c1bbf90de8fb7016f1996db380e5c3bb4","tid":1141913,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:02:35.000Z","msg":"當無識過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc72fab3dfa4b5bb92a4b60ff673b75ce8a15bef","tid":1141913,"uid":207059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ff2a51c1bbf90de8fb7016f1996db380e5c3bb4","tid":1141913,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:02:35.000Z","msg":"當無識過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:04:38.000Z","msg":"我都想，但係我當佢地係唯一嘅朋友，佢地居然咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed632a04956bf9d0e21288a4aa1ce4da2cc1967b","tid":1141913,"uid":118647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8078d1436ad6b93c2404ccead9ed50e142766476","tid":1141913,"uid":207059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0cd0bb8c2902119d49945ec101cef7882331f4d","tid":1141913,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T19:58:40.000Z","msg":"抵啦，好過比人呃十幾萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"十幾萬買唔買到友情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:05:10.000Z","msg":"友情強求唔黎 要走就由佢去 可能咁先見到更好既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78c4343f3fd7ee4ccf744e270efefc597700e51","tid":1141913,"uid":207059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed632a04956bf9d0e2128