n.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:23:56.000Z","msg":"佢地～何來唯一？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bbf3b3435cac63a996d389f354a83f1081423e","tid":1141913,"uid":245957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:26:02.000Z","msg":"無朋友好過 假朋友"},{"pid":"b1a823882a3d31a6ffc5c3dad2c2686525e8f65c","tid":1141913,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:27:35.000Z","msg":"契弟走得摩"},{"pid":"399a3033ee0141d4541c9eb0c7324d5ab8d22298","tid":1141913,"uid":72597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T20:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫嘢咩都由我話事，<span style=\"color: red;\">我當時冇留意</span>，就求其叫咗幾支麥卡倫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你以後要留意下，呢度你有責任。<br />\n<br />\n就算叫得你話事，你都應該禮貌上問聲佢哋，同時避免中伏<br />\n當然佢哋自己畀唔起又畀你話事係佢哋問題<br />\n但肯夾錢係人情，唔畀始終係道理<br />\n就算係父母對仔女都未必係無條件付出，何況朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}